node.text: For the latest installment of “Invite Only”, @hypebeastjp’s @yvkiabe linked up with multi-hyphenate Poggy to chat about his latest pick up, including the @adidasoriginals NMD S1, celebratory @newbalance 990, a bag by @larrysmith_official, and upcycled denim by @proletareart.

node.text: The highly-anticipated album is now set to release on August 15. The date was confirmed by an iTunes album preview page. The album was predicted to release following the end of ’Ye’s second listening event but to no surprise no album was released. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to get the “whoopity-scoop.”

node.text: Skateboarding made its debut at the summer Olympics in Tokyo and we took a look at some of the best moments, how its spotlighting streetwear, and how the addition of new sports is connecting with the younger audience.

node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.

node.text: Founded by Jeff Bezos, space travel company Blue Origin completed its first passenger flight on July 20. The rocket, named New Shepard, carried Bezos and three other passengers more than 65-miles above Earth, just to the boundary of space, known as the Kármán line. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to learn more.

node.title: @jeffbezos Completes His First Flight into Space

node.text: @gucci unveils inaugural ‘Fashion Haul’ episode for its new web series in partnership with HYPEBEAST - bringing together prominent figures to break down the luxury house’s latest designs and exploring subcultures through the world of user-generated online streaming. This episode focuses on the House’s 25 Eschatology styles as well as the new #GucciBasket sneakers.

Our first ever @hypegolf Invitational in Miami took place on May 13 and brought together the best in style, music, entertainment, food, and, of course, golf. Stay tuned for the next one in a city near you.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on August 13, 2021 tagging @champagnepapi, @taylormadegolf, and @hypegolf. May be an image of text that says 'HYPEBEAST NOCTA® P -790 790 rocTa' NOCTA DRAKE TEASES NOCTA- NOCTA-BRANDED TAYLORMADE P790 IRONS Ahead of the irons' hird-generation launch in September.'.

node.text:
@hypegolf: Is @champagnepapi a Certified Golf Boy? The rapper took to his stories to tease NOCTA-branded @taylormadegolf P790 irons ahead of their third-generation launch in September which features proprietary technology, SpeedFoam Air, an ultralight urethane foam that lays in the inner part of the forged hollow body fabrication. ⁠
Photo: Drake

@hypebeastmusic: As the week in music comes to a close, we’ve rounded up some of the best new tracks and projects. Highlights include releases from @wizkidayo, @temsbaby, @justinbieber, @boldyjames, @alanthechemist, @vanjess, @iamluckydaye, @nsg_music, and @still_woozy. What are you listening to this weekend?⁠⁠⁠ ⁠⁠⁠
Video: Isabella Chon/HYPEBEAST

node.text:
@hypebeastgaming: @rockstargames is allegedly working on remastering three classic Grand Theft Auto games. The remaster is reportedly in the final stages of development and will focus on Grand Theft III, Vice City and San Andreas. Aside from updating the UI, the remastered trilogy is expected to feature a mix of new and old graphics via the Unreal Engine to stay true to the originals.⁠
Photo: Rockstar⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on August 13, 2021 tagging @travisscott, @jockograves, and @hypebeastkicks. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: @travisscott recently took to his Instagram Story to tease an unreleased Air Jordan 1 Low. Swipe to take a look and stay tuned for official details. Are you excited for another Travis shoe? ⁠⁠
Photo: @jockograves/Travis Scott

Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on August 12, 2021 tagging @mouaath.m, @mvzzi, @junaynaah, @hypebeaststyle, @wiz_khalifeh, @zeyaanah, @film.byrhys, and @hypebeastarabia. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, headscarf and text that says 'HYPEBEAST JUNAYNAH, ZEYAANAH AND MODEST STREETWEAR The Yemeni sisters talk to us about the world of modest fashion today.'.

node.text:
@hypebeaststyle: The @hypebeastarabia team linked up with Yemeni sisters @zeyaanah and @junaynaah to talk about societal pressures in the Middle East, the evolution of modest streetwear, and more. ⁠Swipe to check it out.⁠⁠
Photos: @wiz_khalifeh/@mvzzi/@mouaath.m/@film.byrhys/Zeyaanah/Junaynah

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on August 12, 2021 tagging @mouaath.m, @mvzzi, @junaynaah, @hypebeaststyle, @wiz_khalifeh, @zeyaanah, @film.byrhys, and @hypebeastarabia. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, headscarf and text that says 'HYPEBEAST JUNAYNAH, ZEYAANAH AND MODEST STREETWEAR The Yemeni sisters talk to us about the world of modest fashion today.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'HYPEBEAST " I've always known who was, the values stood for and how wanted to be perceived while also understanding the role modesty would play in my life, but struggled to see how both worlds fused and in reality they didn' fuse because the older interpretation of modesty clashed with my fundamental principles.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'HYPEBEAST " In the Middle East, there's so much pressure and an obsession to be perfect, proper, socially acceptable and on trend that we almost don't allow ourselves to discover who we are at our core to then express ourselves thoroughly. What is streetwear culture without genuine expression?'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'HYPEBEAST HItDA " I felt as though I didn't have any modest representation of the style that felt made me look best. With the evolution of streetwear, think almost every style has the capability to be modest.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'THE TH ゴ0 一 HYPEBEAST BEAST တာက၀0 " A tip would give someone that's trying to explore modest fashion is to think of "modest fashion' as less of a category on its own, but an addition to the style that you're already aiming for. This way any style can be considered "modest streetwear/fashion".'.

node.text:
#hypeAF: The Perseid meteor shower happens every year from July 23 to August 22. However, it usually reaches its peak from midnight on August 11 to dawn on August 13. The best place to view the spectacle is anywhere in the Northern Hemisphere. In this region, stargazers can expect to see more than 40 meteors per hour if they're far away from light population, according to @nasa. City-dwellers and those located in the Southern Hemisphere may only be able to see a few meteors per hour. ⁠
Photo: NASA/Bill Ingalls

@hypebeastcarclub: As time has shown, the rarity of @ford's GT has driven prices through the roof. That's no exception here for this 2019 Ford GT Heritage Edition with just 46 miles on the clock, that just sold for $1.2 million USD via @bringatrailer. This particular model features a Heritage Roundell Graphics pack which comes together to mimic the famous Gulf livery that graced GT40s back in the late ’60s when they raced at Le Mans. Hit the link in bio to learn more.⁠⁠

@hypebeastkicks: @adidas has sold @reebok to @abg_nyc for a whopping $2.5 Billion USD. Reebok was first brought under the adidas umbrella back in 2006 when the entity was acquired them for $3.6 Billion USD. And while in most recent years Reebok started to make bigger waves across the industry, it doesn’t seem as though it performed well enough. Hit the link in bio for more info.⁠
